{"tid":2450614,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［特權階級］中聯辦及西區警署獲封區豁免","createTime":"2021-03-17T13:57:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T14:36:16.000Z","uid":303304,"like":9,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2c4aa89b755a9b0d6d6cad01db37401d71411c2d","tid":2450614,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T13:57:32.000Z","msg":"政府今晚宣佈圍封西環均益大廈三期，<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"gold\">該處毗鄰的中聯辦及西區警署則未受影響</span></strong></span>；不過同一晚政府於銅鑼灣的圍封行動中，其中一幢海宮大廈因有確診個案而被圍封，但毗鄰的海都大廈雖沒有確診個案或污水樣本呈陽性也被圍封。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210317/BZMVXSF2JZEPJOAJ2TMIJ6EEWE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210317%2FBZMVXSF2JZEPJOAJ2TMIJ6EEWE%2F&d=V7AID%2B4Ek1BfB0hSL70CT4kJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=a28aec31\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210317%2FBZMVXSF2JZEPJOAJ2TMIJ6EEWE%2F&h=18f8b1bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210317/BZMVXSF2JZEPJOAJ2TMIJ6EEWE/</a>"},{"pid":"7a7c4d6e3d07e35c2cd18a29c6d54c80ab37c5c1","tid":2450614,"uid":303304,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T13:58:06.000Z","msg":"油尖旺區議會副主席余德寶表示，以往政府多次在油尖旺圍封時，<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"gold\">曾連沒確診個案或污水呈陽性的大廈，也納入圍封範圍內</span></strong></span>，「兩幢有確診個案嘅大廈，中間嗰幢冇，都俾人封」；他指政府須解釋現時圍封準則是否改變，「係唔係用咗新標準，改咗玩法？」"},{"pid":"02a56b3df8cfad13dfac4b7f5ecb3500b2ee3b4a","tid":2450614,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T13:59:08.000Z","msg":"今晚政府圍封有確診個案的均益大廈，指因該處有確診個案，加上樓齡較舊及多劏房，<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"gold\">經評估後相關區域感染風險有機會較高。</span></span></strong>而在均益大廈旁邊、相隔只有約100公尺的中聯辦則倖免。"},{"pid":"1ccf7ce79316cd5f426ca1d33a7f76e3eaa0750f","tid":2450614,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T14:01:01.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d2c11d13bb2a9fba651ee6641644134f84ed4c45","tid":24